headline: 5 P&C Insurance Stocks to Watch Amid Increased Digitalization
summary: Zacks Property and Casualty Insurance players like BRK.B, PGR, CB, TRV and ALL are likely to benefit from digitalization and catastrophes that drive policy renewal rate and pricing.

headline: RNR Q2 Earnings Beat on Strong Property Underwriting Results
summary: RenaissanceRe's Q2 earnings benefit from strong Property underwriting results and lower net claims and claim expenses incurred, partly offset by declining net premiums earned in the Casualty & Specialty unit.
